  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个医疗科技系统的架构图，核心是解决患者记录管理和诊断引擎之间的资金流转问题。我设想有一个智能合约层来处理服务扣费。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，您说的是类似按使用量计费的模式？那HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine作为发起方，HealthTech_PatientRecords作为合约中枢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，DiagnosticEngine调用服务时会产生费用。PatientRecords在这里既是用户账户的抽象，也是计费合约的核心节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，我把这个合约子图命名为\"service smart contract\"，里面用µpay节点代表PatientRecords合约。然后DiagnosticEngine以负费率-0.1扣费，PatientRecords服务以+0.1入账，这样设计可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "µpay",
        "User0",
        "Service0",
        "dt = -0.1",
        "dt = +0.1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "费率标注很清晰。但除了DiagnosticEngine，还需要EMR_Sync和另一个PatientRecords实例作为资金去向，代表不同服务的结算路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User1",
        "Service1",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加。现在µpay向下连接到User1(HealthTech_EMR_Sync)和Service1(HealthTech_PatientRecords)，形成完整的合约内流转。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "µpay",
        "User1",
        "Service1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "合约层之外，还需要一个独立的提现子系统。医生或实验室需要把赚到的代币提取出来，这个流程要隔离在合约外。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "withdrawal",
        "tx3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "提现子图用\"withdrawal\"命名，核心节点是tx3？它应该代表具体的提现交易？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "withdrawal",
        "tx3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，tx3是提现交易的中转站。LabAnalyzer作为资金来源方，HIPAA_Vault作为安全存储，最终流向DiagnosticEngine完成提现。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "tx3",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "withdrawal子图已构建：User1(HealthTech_LabAnalyzer)和Service1(HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault)汇入tx3，再分发到User2(LabAnalyzer)、Service2(EMR_Sync)，以及标注withdrawal的Service3(DiagnosticEngine)。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "tx3",
        "User1",
        "Service1",
