        "Service3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这里有个问题——User1在合约层已经是EMR_Sync了，在提现层怎么变成LabAnalyzer了？角色冲突了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User1",
