    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "抱歉，我混淆了角色映射。修正：withdrawal子图中的User1应该独立定义为HealthTech_LabAnalyzer，与合约层的EMR_Sync区分开。两个子图的User1是不同实例。",
      "elements_involved": [
