      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "是的，User0(DiagnosticEngine)在合约层通过-0.1费率支出，Service3(DiagnosticEngine)在提现层通过withdrawal标签接收资金，这是同一机构在不同阶段的不同角色。",
